HIV pixel clustering and cell clustering, no normalization (no frequency normalization, no calibration channel)

Candace Liu

January 18, 2021

  • No frequency normalization or calibration before pixel clustering
  • Gaussian blur sigma=2, k=20 (pixel metaclusters)
  • z-score cap=3 for hierarchical clustering
  • k=20 (cell metaclusters)
